stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Draft
  Draft --> InProgress: start survey
  InProgress --> ReadyToUpload: mark complete
  ReadyToUpload --> Uploaded: publish
  Uploaded --> AcceptedServer: intake accepted
  Uploaded --> UploadFailed: network/error
  UploadFailed --> ReadyToUpload: retry
  AcceptedServer --> InReview: reviewer starts
  InReview --> Completed: compliance + next steps
  AcceptedServer --> RejectedByIntake: validation/dedup failure
  RejectedByIntake --> InProgress: correct + republish
